Configuration file syntax [may be modified later]

currently only UDP protocol is supported [that's really needed in DSE].

----------------$(CFGDIR)/addrs.cfg----------
N
ip-address1
ip-address2
...
ip-addressN
--------------------------------------------

----------------$(CFGDIR)/ports.cfg-----------
N
port1
port2
...
portN
---------------------------------------------------


The above configuration file says that ip-addressN should get UDP broadcasts
on ports specified following it.

